						<h3 itemprop="name" class="not-hidden">
					Philemon Morara Apiemi			</h3>
		<div itemprop="articleBody">
		<p>Mr. Philemon Morara Apiemi LL.B (Hons), Dip in Law (KSL), Certified Public Secretary of Kenya (CPS (K)), Associate of the Insurance Institute of India (ACII), Member of the Chartered Institute of Arbitrators (MCIArb), BSL (Hons). He is an Advocate of the High Court of Kenya, a member of the Law Society of Kenya and an accomplished legal practitioner and Researcher.</p>
<p>He is the managing partner of Morara Apiemi &amp; Nyangito Advocates and in charge of Conveyancing, Civil Litigation, Insurance, Banking and Arbitration. He is a Kenyan National. He was admitted in the Roll of Advocates in 2000.</p> 	</div>

	
	
				
	
	
